title: 150 messages per day
info:
150 messages for 1 day for the price of 2  Afghani. 
Press the green button to activate and the red button to deactivate. 
Send 6 to activate and 5 to deactivate to 676

title: 1000 messages per day
info:
1000 messages for 1 day at the price of 15 Afghanis. 
To activate, press the green button  And press the red button to deactivate. 
Send 4 to activate and 5 to deactivate to 676
